data.text:
May 07, 1993 was a Friday and it was the 127th day of the year 1993 in the Gregorian calendar.

May 07, 1993 can also be written as 5/7/1993 in the US and as 7/5/1993 in UK and Europe.

The Zodiac and Astrological sign for May 7th is Taurus.

Moon phase

The moon phase on May 07, 1993 was Full Moon.

The moon phase refers to the appearance of the Moon in the night sky on May 07, 1993 and is determined by the portion of the Moon's illuminated surface that is visible from Earth.

An observer located in New York City on May 07, 1993 at 10pm, would see the moon, being 93% full, rising at 08:57 pm and setting at 07:37 am.

The previous full moon was on May 06, 1993 while the next full moon would come on Jun 04, 1993.

What is special about May 7th?

May 7th refers to a specific date on the calendar, which is the 7th day of the month of May. It is a date that occurs annually and is part of the Gregorian calendar, which is widely used around the world.

Over the years several events happened on May 7th, such as:

2019 - Second libyan civil war 2019, 2019 western libya offensive: a pro-gna mirage f1 fighter plane was shot down by the libyan national army over tripoli. the pilot, who claimed to be portuguese but his identity could not be confirmed by the portuguese ministry of foreign affairs, was captured and taken into custody. the lna's media outlet released photos showing the injured pilot flanked and assisted by lna officials.

2018 - Yemeni civil war (2015)-present: saudi-led coalition airstrikes destroy sana'a presidential palace, yemen. at least six people were killed and 30 injured. officials from the coalition claim that they targeted high-ranking houthi officials.

2017 - After a collision between a truck and bus in vietnam's gia lai province, at least 11 people have been killed.
